metadata.title: SIMPLY NOURISH Puppy Salmon and Sweet Potato Dry Dog Food, 4 lbs and Especiales Cosas Mixing Spatula
features: One bag of Simply Nourish puppy dry dog food - Salmon and Sweet Potato Recipe (4 Pound Bag) and Especiales Cosas Mixing Spatula bundle
This 4 pound bag of dry dog food that is formulated for puppies, all breeds, and comes packaged in a four (4) pound bag
One 7 inch Especiales Cosas plastic mixing spatula (colors may vary). The spatula can be used for mixing water in with the dry food, adding toppings, etc.
Real deboned salmon is the first ingredient in this delicious dry dog food. This food does not contain potatoes, grains or chicken
description: Simply Nourish limited ingredient Salmon and Sweet Potato dry dog food for puppies and Especiales Cosas Mixing Spatula bundle. One 4 (four) pound bag of dry dog food.
